These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: carrot, raspberry
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food   | carrot  | raspberry |
| Beverage     | cola | fanta  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, turkish
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Beverage    | cola      | mirinda         |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: billiard, snooker
There are 2 different nationalities: german, russian
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Game   | snooker | billiard   |
| Nationality       | russian  | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
