.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, tennis
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, country
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Sport      | lacrosse | tennis |
| Music-Genre   | country        | dubstep  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
