.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-7::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, alhambra
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | montecristo | alhambra |
| Flower      | lily     | amaryllis  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-8::.
